":"Author/Piotr Kaczmarczyk","line":80},{"title":"Author/Ewa Nogaj","target":"Author/Ewa Nogaj","line":81},{"title":"Author/Ewa Nogaj","target":"Author/Ewa Nogaj","line":82},{"title":"Author/Jacek Piętka","target":"Author/Jacek Piętka","line":83},{"title":"Author/Jacek Piętka","target":"Author/Jacek Piętka","line":84},{"title":"PDF","target":"biblib/muszynska_fomitopsis_2020/muszynska_fomitopsis_2020.pdf","line":86}],"metadata":{"id":"muszynska_fomitopsis_2020","type":"article-journal","title":"Fomitopsis officinalis: a Species of Arboreal Mushroom with Promising Biological and Medicinal Properties","issued":{"date-parts":[[2020]]},"DOI":"10.1002/cbdv.202000213","container-title":"Chemistry & Biodiversity","abstract":"Medicinal mushrooms of the order Polyporales have a long history of use, which is evidenced by the finding of dissected fruiting bodies with Otzi, who lived over 5000 years ago. Because of its valuable biological properties and its use in 18th and 19th-century pharmacy, Fomitopsis officinalis used to be mass-collected. Moreover, the large demand for larch wood and non-wood materials (resin) caused an excessive exploitation of larch forests, which directly contributed to the disappearance of F. officinalis from its natural environment. The qualities of medicinal preparations obtained from the F. officinalis fruiting bodies are determined by the unique composition of its bioactive compounds, such as: triterpenoids, polysaccharides, organic acids, coumarins and phenolic compounds. It has been proved that both crude extracts and the compounds isolated from F. officinalis have a wide spectrum of therapeutic effects, including anti-inflammatory, cytotoxic, and antimicrobial effects.","tags":["#literature_note"],"author":[{"family":"Muszyńska","given":"Bożena","literal":""},{"family":"Muszyńska","given":"Bożena","literal":""},{"family":"Fijałkowska","given":"Agata","literal":""},{"family":"Fijałkowska","given":"Agata","literal":""},{"family":"Fijałkowska","given":"Agata","literal":""},{"family":"Sułkowska-Ziaja","given":"Katarzyna","literal":""},{"family":"Sułkowska-Ziaja","given":"Katarzyna","literal":""},{"family":"Włodarczyk","given":"Anna","literal":""},{"family":"Wlodarczyk","given":"Anna","literal":""},{"family":"Wlodarczyk","given":"Anna Julia","literal":""},{"family":"Kaczmarczyk","given":"Piotr","literal":""},{"family":"Kaczmarczyk","given":"Piotr","literal":""},{"family":"Nogaj","given":"Ewa","literal":""},{"family":"Nogaj","given":"Ewa","literal":""},{"family":"Piętka","given":"Jacek","literal":""},{"family":"Piętka","given":"Jacek","literal":""}],"citation-key":"muszynska_fomitopsis_2020","year":"2020","dateCreated":"2026-03-31","reading-status":"to-read","aliases":["Fomitopsis officinalis: a Species of Arboreal Mushroom with Promising Biological and Medicinal Properties"],"author-links":["[[Author/Bożena Muszyńska]]","[[Author/Bożena Muszyńska]]","[[Author/Agata Fijałkowska]]","[[Author/Agata Fijałkowska]]","[[Author/Agata Fijałkowska]]","[[Author/Katarzyna Sułkowska-Ziaja]]","[[Author/Katarzyna Sułkowska-Ziaja]]","[[Author/Anna Włodarczyk]]","[[Author/Anna Wlodarczyk]]","[[Author/Anna Julia Wlodarczyk]]","[[Author/Piotr Kaczmarczyk]]","[[Author/Piotr Kaczmarczyk]]","[[Author/Ewa Nogaj]]","[[Author/Ewa Nogaj]]","[[Author/Jacek Piętka]]","[[Author/Jacek Piętka]]"],"attachment":["[[biblib/muszynska_fomitopsis_2020/muszynska_fomitopsis_2020.pdf|PDF]]"],"related":[[]]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"1wt64rq","at":1774951891237}},"smart_blocks:Research/@muszynska_fomitopsis_2020.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.00457267,-0.04597262,0.05173087,-0.04039426,0.06966259,-0.01481942,0.02795133,0.04269637,-0.04104526,-0.00029092,0.01687773,-0.04512246,-0.03008587,0.01938261,0.01544251,0.03615284,0.03097632,0.01335332,-0.0823514,0.00770093,0.08136738,-0.01571377,0.02055737,0.00661787,0.05431255,0.01837601,-0.02582385,0.00369807,-